original_body_lines: A new political party led by Samagi Jana Balawegaya (SJB) parliamentarian Patali Champika Ranawaka was launched today at the National Youth Center Auditorium. The party named the ‘United Republic Front’ was launched to coincide with Sri Lanka’s Republic Day. The chosen symbol for the new party is the ‘Pencil’. Pix by Kushan Pathiraja
